rule-12-1a.description: Space count in Baseline RMR = User RMR

rule-12-2b.description: Space count in Proposed RMR > User RMR

rule-12-2c.description: Space count in Proposed RMR < User RMR

rule-12-3a.description: User RMR space name is in the Proposed RMR

rule-12-3b.description: User RMR space name is not in the Proposed RMR

rule-12-4b.description: User RMR space name is not in the Baseline RMR

rule-12-5b.description: Space modeled in User RMR, Receptacle Power modeled in the User Model, Proposed RMR doesn't equal User Model RMR

rule-12-6a.description: Space modeled in User RMR, Receptacle Schedule modeled in the User Model, Proposed RMR equals User  RMR

rule-12-6b.description: Space modeled in User RMR, Receptacle Schedule modeled in the User Model, Proposed RMR doesn't equal User Model RMR

rule-12-7a.description: Space modeled in user RMR, Receptacle Power modeled in the User Model, Base RMR equals User  RMR
